<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Ka Lal Nunnem</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal pien hun pakcha a lun kit tai,
 Suihlung ip nung lunghel a kaitho hi;
 Van nuoi mi gen Bethlehem tang chung ah,
 Ginna thân mi a leng kai ui.

[V2]
 Aw ka Lal nunnem naubang ei pui zelin,
 Na chun leh zuo kalah senlai naubang na kahna
 Mun tuol ka ngai.

[V3]
 2. Mubang ka ngai Bethlehem tangpi.
 Sunni muolliem din a salhvak singseng;
 Bawng In tawma ka Lal gen liengthei chu,
 A chun lieng Mari'n a pawm hi.

[V4]
 3. Bethlehem Aksi a vak kit tai.
 Eden than thim dawngkawt a hun salhvak;
 Halh in tho un Eden taikhuo a val,
 I tup gam chu zuon zel hitiu.

[V5]
 4. A hawih nau e! Lalna gam tuolthing,
 Ei di'n Bethlehem tang a lun sak tai;
 Tuona I pi leh puteu muh phak loh,
 Saron pak tanin I leng ui.</lyrics>
<author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>11</hymn_number>
</song>